---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const endpoints = [
  { path: '/codes/<CODE>.json', returns: 'One code record.', sample: '/codes/MH-12.json' },
  { path: '/states/<STATE_CODE>.json', returns: 'All codes in one state.', sample: '/states/MH.json' },
  { path: '/states.json', returns: 'List of every state/UT with code counts.', sample: '/states.json' },
  { path: '/index.json', returns: 'Compact array of every code string. Use for autocomplete.', sample: '/index.json' },
  { path: '/all.json', returns: 'Every full record in one file (~200 KB).', sample: '/all.json' },
];
---
<Layout title="API docs &mdash; Indian RTO Codes" path="/docs">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pt-16 pb-8">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-saffron-600 dark:text-saffron-400">Reference</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">API documentation</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">All endpoints are static JSON files. No authentication, no rate limiting, no SDK required. Fetch them with anything that speaks HTTP.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-8">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500">Endpoints</h2>
    <div class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead class="bg-zinc-50 text-left dark:bg-zinc-900/50">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">Path</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">Returns</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">Sample</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-200 dark:divide-zinc-800">
          {endpoints.map((e) => (
            <tr>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-saffron-700 dark:text-saffron-400">{e.path}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">{e.returns}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3"><a href={e.sample} class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-600 underline decoration-zinc-400 underline-offset-4 hover:text-saffron-600 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:text-saffron-400" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{e.sample}</a></td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500">Base URL: <code class="font-mono text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">https://rto.oriz.in</code> &middot; also available at <code class="font-mono text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/oriz-org/rto-api@main</code></p>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-8">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500">Record schema</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">Each <code class="font-mono text-saffron-700 dark:text-saffron-400">/codes/&lt;CODE&gt;.json</code> file returns one record:</p>
    <pre class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 p-4 text-sm dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900"><code class="font-mono text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200">type RtoCode = {`{`}
  code:       string;   // e.g. "MH-12"
  state_code: string;   // 2-letter prefix, e.g. "MH"
  state:      string;   // expanded name, e.g. "Maharashtra"
  office:     string;   // RTO office city / location (may be empty)
  district:   string;   // jurisdiction (may be empty)
  notes:      string;   // annotation (may be empty)
{`}`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-8">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500">Special cases</h2>
    <div class="mt-4 space-y-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-saffron-700 dark:text-saffron-400">AP-39 / AP-40 &mdash; one-state-one-code</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">Andhra Pradesh consolidated to a single registration code in Feb 2019. These records replace <code class="font-mono">district</code> with a <code class="font-mono">districts: string[]</code> array.</p>
        <pre class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto rounded bg-zinc-50 p-3 text-xs dark:bg-zinc-900"><code class="font-mono">{`{
  "code": "AP-39",
  "state_code": "AP",
  "office": "RTA",
  "districts": ["Tirupati district", "Krishna district", "..."],
  "notes": "One state-one code policy from Feb 2019. ..."
}`}</code></pre>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-saffron-700 dark:text-saffron-400">AS-20, AS-30, CG-01 &mdash; fleet / police codes</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">Some codes are reserved for state-owned fleets (e.g. State Transport Corporation buses) or police vehicles. The <code class="font-mono">district</code> field carries the operator name; the <code class="font-mono">office</code> field may be empty.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-8">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500">Errors</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">The only possible error is <code class="font-mono text-saffron-700 dark:text-saffron-400">404</code> &mdash; unknown code. There is no authentication, no rate limit, and no quota, so 401/403/429 cannot occur. CORS is wide open on both origins (Cloudflare Pages and jsDelivr).</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-8">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500">License</h2>
    <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
      <li><strong class="font-semibold">Code</strong> (<code class="font-mono">scripts/</code>, build tooling): <a class="underline decoration-saffron-500/40 underline-offset-4 hover:text-saffron-700 dark:hover:text-saffron-400" href="https://github.com/oriz-org/rto-api/blob/main/LICENSE">MIT</a></li>
      <li><strong class="font-semibold">Data</strong> (<code class="font-mono">codes/</code>, <code class="font-mono">states/</code>, <code class="font-mono">*.json</code>): <a class="underline decoration-saffron-500/40 underline-offset-4 hover:text-saffron-700 dark:hover:text-saffron-400" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/">CC BY-SA 4.0</a> (inherited from Wikipedia)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500">Attribution: &quot;Source: Wikipedia / List of Regional Transport Office districts in India&quot;.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
